        PixeLINKds Changelog
        ====================
        
        0.1 (2016-08-25)
        ----------------
        
        - First public release.
        - Implemented a Reader for homogeneous Pixelink Data Stream file.
        - Implemented Frame Descriptor based on ctypes structure.
        
